{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：18:27 2026-05-03 HKT<br/>發佈時間：18:27 2026-05-03 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：18:27 2026-05-03 HKT</p><img alt=\"「首飾天空」大熱奪標\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl_square/daa518552633ad174d49edeca0778b87/2026-05/r8_0.jpg\"/><p>今日沙田馬場另一場錦標賽，二班千六米會員盃，蔡約翰馬房的「首飾天空」被捧成一面倒大熱門，該駒亦發揮岀馬迷預期水準，由艾兆禮策騎後上贏馬，廄侶「永遠美麗」跑第二，構成一條馬房連贏位，艾兆禮則連續十五次沙田賽事取得勝利。</p><h2>按下圖睇更多相片：</h2><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/d89ce405da75fa951495b3565286f550/2026-05/5c5c9fd0-db04-4d93-8a63-ba263368fa0e.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/d29117bd282f43ab889ccf974b3f37b7/2026-05/6bd3c093-54e3-40ba-86cf-053e4bfcbde1.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/13e9fee071c8fe0e89aec3df9d1b8a76/2026-05/31ba3ce0-117a-4cd8-8f96-c392c4d12f79.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/5731dbc47db0a4b610d28448a6097fee/2026-05/54c30c9d-39f0-4ad2-aac5-0d644d18c63b.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9699bdfeae20ee56f814ab101898128e/2026-05/94a3548c-f07a-45c7-b8e2-c50ab235416f.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/4f1eae6e21ec897061ed44cdda8b4b7f/2026-05/972e53d9-7ad3-4965-819d-33dcec381ede.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/2bff5531285cfa54290b2ac660831772/2026-05/6535ecff-b02d-4d6c-8b3f-c57eef8f5f83.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/4139761d673393a6af41dcd0d6882d1a/2026-05/6446244b-24af-4a50-96b5-8fc92f150996.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/ecf4ff7873a7af02cc0ce81fa7042373/2026-05/a0b75989-1df4-40d4-a159-84633af13eb8.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/1d5c6d9e5f78807f86b68163573214c5/2026-05/b3aa99c6-34e7-4cd7-a8f9-000c201dca4e.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/d7056c0e453ba249f04724234d33b4a9/2026-05/b04f065a-0e65-4920-887a-4c5eed45f5c2.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/81510a0564a03cb4e